{"questionId":"9076265","questionHtml":"<p>The lens is 18 cm from the screen and the image is 0.40 times smaller than the object. Calculate the power of the lens, in cm<sup>–1</sup>.&nbsp;</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>«</strong><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" - \\frac{{18}}{u} = &nbsp;- 0.40\">\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>18</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mi>u</mi>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>0.40</mn>\n</math></span>»</p>\n<p><em>u</em> = 45</p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{1}{{45}} + \\frac{1}{{18}} = \\frac{1}{f}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mn>1</mn>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>45</mn>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mn>1</mn>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>18</mn>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mn>1</mn>\n    <mi>f</mi>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p><strong><em>OR</em></strong></p>\n<p><em>f</em> = 13&nbsp;<strong>«</strong>cm<strong>»</strong></p>\n<p><em>P</em> =&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{1}{f}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mn>1</mn>\n    <mi>f</mi>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span> =&nbsp;<strong>«</strong><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{1}{{13}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mn>1</mn>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>13</mn>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span><strong>»</strong> = 0.078 <strong>«</strong>cm<sup>–1</sup><strong>»</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em>Accept answer 7.7</em><strong><em>«</em></strong><em>D</em><strong><em>».</em></strong></p>\n<p><strong><em>[3 marks]</em></strong></p>","meta":{"questionId":"9076265","referenceCode":"18M.3.SL.TZ1.a.ii","subjectId":"46-dp-physics-last-assessment-2024","title":"The lens is 18 cm from the screen and the image is 0.40 times smaller than the object. Calculate the power of the lens, in cm–1.","paper":"3","level":"SL","questionNumber":"a.ii","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 3]","breadcrumbLabels":["Option C: Imaging","Option C: Imaging","Option C: Imaging (Core topics)","C.1 – Introduction to imaging","Option C: Imaging","Option C: Imaging (Core topics)"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}